00:03:35.560 --> 00:03:37.910
[the new Emperor Li Shu
was long ill and absent from court.]

00:03:37.910 --> 00:03:40.190
[Empress Zhou Ruoxi
took charge of state affairs,]

00:03:40.190 --> 00:03:41.340
[bestowing favors in his name.]

