Capture the evil empress!

00:04:22.470 --> 00:04:23.680
Long time no see,

00:04:24.560 --> 00:04:26.040
Prince Yan.

00:04:38.690 --> 00:04:40.150
Do you also want to kill me?

00:04:40.710 --> 00:04:42.730
Don't you want
to beg me to spare your life?

00:04:42.730 --> 00:04:44.050
Prince Yan, you know

00:04:45.150 --> 00:04:47.030
I am not that kind of person.

00:04:48.680 --> 00:04:49.470
Yes,

00:04:52.540 --> 00:04:53.800
I certainly know that.

00:05:01.280 --> 00:05:02.410
Where is my brother?

00:05:03.000 --> 00:05:04.160
I don't know.

00:05:06.720 --> 00:05:07.860
His Majesty was gravely ill.

00:05:07.860 --> 00:05:09.860
After entrusting the throne to me,

00:05:10.090 --> 00:05:11.410
he disappeared.

00:05:11.890 --> 00:05:12.890
Wasn't it you

00:05:13.450 --> 00:05:15.180
who made my brother disappear?

00:05:15.640 --> 00:05:16.720
This throne

00:05:17.380 --> 00:05:18.440
is truly splendid.

00:05:18.700 --> 00:05:19.860
Do you want it?

00:05:19.980 --> 00:05:21.730
When was the last time

00:05:21.910 --> 00:05:23.060
you saw my brother?

00:05:23.080 --> 00:05:24.500
But I want it.

00:05:26.500 --> 00:05:27.860
Will you help me?

00:05:28.070 --> 00:05:28.930
You've gone mad.

00:05:28.930 --> 00:05:30.170
I am not mad.

00:05:32.560 --> 00:05:34.840
Since I received it from His Majesty,

00:05:35.510 --> 00:05:36.780
I've worked day and night,

00:05:36.780 --> 00:05:38.580
exhausting myself completely.

00:05:38.670 --> 00:05:40.280
Everything I've done

00:05:40.880 --> 00:05:43.200
has been for the realm of Yunrui.

00:05:44.250 --> 00:05:45.090
His Majesty

00:05:45.840 --> 00:05:47.000
could sit on this throne.

00:05:47.000 --> 00:05:48.740
Your Li clan could seize it.

00:05:49.070 --> 00:05:50.600
By what right am I denied it?

00:05:53.220 --> 00:05:53.810
Li Yan,

00:05:54.220 --> 00:05:55.300
tell me,

00:05:55.330 --> 00:05:57.190
why am I not worthy of this throne?

00:05:57.690 --> 00:05:58.720
Zhou Ruoxi,

00:05:59.850 --> 00:06:00.950
I thought

00:06:01.560 --> 00:06:02.840
you abandoned our love

00:06:02.880 --> 00:06:03.580
and pursued power

00:06:03.580 --> 00:06:05.630
because circumstances forced you to.

00:06:05.630 --> 00:06:06.730
But now I see

00:06:07.010 --> 00:06:08.890
you've truly lost your way.

00:06:09.160 --> 00:06:10.290
Is that not allowed?

00:06:14.590 --> 00:06:16.320
I'm done with a life

00:06:16.690 --> 00:06:18.420
of groveling and humiliation.

00:06:18.960 --> 00:06:19.600
I will

00:06:20.650 --> 00:06:22.580
never live like that again.

00:06:26.810 --> 00:06:27.610
Come with me.

00:06:38.990 --> 00:06:40.110
Just kill me.

00:06:40.420 --> 00:06:41.570
Zhou Ruoxi!

00:06:50.220 --> 00:06:51.880
This is your last chance.

00:06:56.570 --> 00:06:58.050
Don't force my hand.

00:07:22.670 --> 00:07:24.080
I've struggled so hard

00:07:26.080 --> 00:07:27.260
to get where I am.

00:07:41.130 --> 00:07:43.260
I am the Empress of Yunrui.

00:07:45.010 --> 00:07:45.970
I will

00:07:46.620 --> 00:07:47.900
not leave.

00:07:55.090 --> 00:07:56.090
Prince Yan, if you

00:07:56.350 --> 00:07:57.750
cannot bear to kill me...

00:08:00.610 --> 00:08:01.560
Then go.

00:09:43.270 --> 00:09:44.600
Xi, don't blame me.

00:09:46.440 --> 00:09:48.040
Only if the evil empress dies

00:09:49.200 --> 00:09:50.970
can Zhou Ruoxi live.

00:10:01.720 --> 00:10:03.530
How did we end up like this?

00:10:05.140 --> 00:10:06.540
Have you truly forgotten

00:10:08.120 --> 00:10:09.780
all those memories we shared?

00:10:10.630 --> 00:10:12.420
Prince Yan, you accepted my sachet,

00:10:12.420 --> 00:10:14.080
which means we're betrothed.

00:10:18.280 --> 00:10:19.690
To avenge my mother,

00:10:20.250 --> 00:10:22.650
I can only rely on
the Crown Prince's power.

00:10:23.520 --> 00:10:24.370
Prince Yan,

00:10:25.450 --> 00:10:26.850
you cannot give me these.

00:10:45.360 --> 00:10:46.410
Don't move.

00:10:48.210 --> 00:10:49.620
Why did you save me?

00:10:49.740 --> 00:10:51.270
I told you I wouldn't leave.

00:10:51.780 --> 00:10:53.440
I am the Empress of Yunrui.

00:10:54.160 --> 00:10:56.490
I will wait here
for His Majesty to return.

00:11:01.880 --> 00:11:03.320
The Empress of Yunrui

00:11:03.340 --> 00:11:04.540
is there.

00:11:04.730 --> 00:11:05.530
Li Yan.

00:11:06.570 --> 00:11:07.900
What are you going to do?

00:11:08.170 --> 00:11:08.970
Zhou Ruoxi.

00:11:09.670 --> 00:11:10.800
You should thank me.

00:11:12.560 --> 00:11:15.560
I arranged for a death row prisoner
to take your place.

00:11:15.920 --> 00:11:16.860
Otherwise,

00:11:17.930 --> 00:11:19.590
at today's execution by fire,

00:11:20.830 --> 00:11:21.990
you would be the one dying.

00:11:21.990 --> 00:11:22.870
No!

00:11:23.650 --> 00:11:24.840
It's not like that.

00:11:25.420 --> 00:11:26.480
It's not like that.

00:11:26.490 --> 00:11:27.380
It's not like that.

00:11:27.380 --> 00:11:28.100
Don't move.

00:11:28.670 --> 00:11:31.330
You need to witness
your fate with your own eyes.

00:11:35.960 --> 00:11:37.160
Execute the evil empress!

00:11:37.160 --> 00:11:38.680
Safeguard peace!

