Execute the evil empress!

00:11:45.750 --> 00:11:47.110
Safeguard peace!

00:11:47.130 --> 00:11:48.620
Execute the evil empress!

00:11:48.640 --> 00:11:50.160
Safeguard peace!

00:11:58.530 --> 00:11:59.330
Whoa!

00:12:00.320 --> 00:12:01.180
Who goes there?

00:12:05.080 --> 00:12:08.800
[Qingzhou]

00:12:10.940 --> 00:12:11.980
Yan!

00:12:12.770 --> 00:12:13.900
What a coincidence.

00:12:15.200 --> 00:12:17.490
You've done great service
in defense of the throne.

00:12:17.490 --> 00:12:19.950
Why not wait
for your reward before leaving?

00:12:20.800 --> 00:12:21.800
Brother, I heard that you've been

00:12:21.800 --> 00:12:23.220
suffering from a long illness

00:12:23.220 --> 00:12:24.340
and couldn't even leave your bed.

00:12:24.340 --> 00:12:26.210
And then you vanished without a trace.

00:12:26.210 --> 00:12:27.300
But now it seems

00:12:27.440 --> 00:12:28.700
that was just a false rumor.

00:12:28.700 --> 00:12:29.750
Your Majesty!

00:12:30.100 --> 00:12:31.450
[Qingzhou]

00:12:32.450 --> 00:12:33.260
Your Majesty!

00:12:34.700 --> 00:12:35.590
Your Majesty!

00:12:35.920 --> 00:12:37.190
You've finally come.

00:12:37.520 --> 00:12:38.440
I...

00:12:38.460 --> 00:12:39.910
The evil Empress Zhou

00:12:40.030 --> 00:12:43.090
was burned at the stake
at the Meridian Gate last night.

00:12:43.890 --> 00:12:44.810
Yan.

00:12:45.410 --> 00:12:47.200
Why is she still alive?

00:12:47.320 --> 00:12:48.120
Your Majesty.

00:12:48.370 --> 00:12:50.250
Zhou Ruoxi's crimes are unforgivable.

00:12:50.250 --> 00:12:51.730
But everything she did

00:12:52.050 --> 00:12:53.790
was for the sake of Yunrui.

00:12:54.330 --> 00:12:56.210
I beg you to spare her life.

00:12:56.940 --> 00:12:59.630
I nurtured her ambition bit by bit,

00:12:59.660 --> 00:13:00.960
all for this day.

00:13:01.730 --> 00:13:03.610
Yet you ask me to spare her?

00:13:03.640 --> 00:13:04.570
Your Majesty.

00:13:07.090 --> 00:13:08.290
You want to kill me?

00:13:08.500 --> 00:13:09.710
Zhou Ruoxi.

00:13:10.130 --> 00:13:12.210
You caused
your elder sister Ruoyao's death.

00:13:12.210 --> 00:13:13.880
You killed the woman I loved most.

00:13:13.880 --> 00:13:15.800
Should I not kill you?

00:13:16.600 --> 00:13:17.520
Yan.

00:13:17.730 --> 00:13:19.360
Kill her now,

00:13:19.860 --> 00:13:21.000
and your merit in serving the throne

00:13:21.000 --> 00:13:22.440
shall remain.

00:13:23.740 --> 00:13:24.740
I cannot

00:13:24.860 --> 00:13:26.620
obey this order.

00:13:32.080 --> 00:13:33.200
Fine.

00:13:33.640 --> 00:13:35.970
Don't blame me for being ruthless.

00:14:04.640 --> 00:14:05.550
Liang Feng!

00:14:53.080 --> 00:14:54.000
Prince Yan!

00:14:58.020 --> 00:14:59.220
Yan!

00:15:03.670 --> 00:15:04.870
Yan!

00:15:11.730 --> 00:15:12.570
Xi.

00:15:14.520 --> 00:15:15.520
It's been so long

00:15:15.900 --> 00:15:17.570
since you called me that.

00:15:32.320 --> 00:15:34.070
If you care for him so deeply,

00:15:34.310 --> 00:15:36.510
why didn't you marry him back then?

00:15:40.940 --> 00:15:42.340
What are you laughing at?

00:15:43.410 --> 00:15:45.920
I laugh at how pitiful Your Majesty is.

00:15:49.820 --> 00:15:52.810
You kept claiming
how much you loved my sister,

00:15:53.920 --> 00:15:55.780
but when her face was disfigured,

00:15:56.080 --> 00:15:58.470
you didn't dare
to propose to her immediately.

00:15:58.470 --> 00:16:00.400
That's how I got the position.

00:16:00.510 --> 00:16:01.440
Li Shu,

00:16:01.820 --> 00:16:02.920
what you love

00:16:03.390 --> 00:16:04.650
and what you care about

00:16:04.750 --> 00:16:06.010
from beginning to end

00:16:07.170 --> 00:16:08.790
has only been yourself.

00:16:08.940 --> 00:16:11.460
What right do you have to accuse me?

00:16:11.790 --> 00:16:13.760
Isn't everything happening now

00:16:13.790 --> 00:16:16.120
your own doing?

00:16:16.200 --> 00:16:16.960
Yes,

00:16:17.400 --> 00:16:19.190
but wasn't everything that led me here

00:16:19.190 --> 00:16:21.440
part of Your Majesty's plan?

00:16:22.080 --> 00:16:24.560
Your Majesty used me
to eliminate the aristocratic clans,

00:16:24.560 --> 00:16:26.820
made me the target of everyone's hatred,

00:16:26.840 --> 00:16:29.370
then used
the aristocratic clans' vengeance

00:16:29.620 --> 00:16:30.900
to kill me.

00:16:30.970 --> 00:16:32.390
After my execution,

00:16:32.410 --> 00:16:34.440
Your Majesty will take over a clean court.

00:16:34.440 --> 00:16:35.640
Shut up!

00:16:38.810 --> 00:16:39.830
Yan,

00:16:40.350 --> 00:16:41.630
I'm sorry.

00:17:29.900 --> 00:17:31.140
Xi.

00:17:39.420 --> 00:17:41.380
I've kept it all this time.

00:17:51.590 --> 00:17:53.100
I got you into this.

00:17:57.520 --> 00:18:00.120
If there's a next life,

00:18:01.620 --> 00:18:02.760
please don't

00:18:08.970 --> 00:18:10.890
meet me again.

00:18:18.730 --> 00:18:19.840
I willingly

00:18:21.140 --> 00:18:22.630
accept

00:18:23.520 --> 00:18:25.440
this fate.

00:18:33.840 --> 00:18:35.240
In my entire life,

00:18:36.010 --> 00:18:37.570
I've schemed and plotted,

00:18:38.800 --> 00:18:40.770
only to end up like this.

00:18:42.900 --> 00:18:44.600
It's unbearable to accept.

